his first automobile from Mecham, who owned and operated a Pontiac
dealership in nearby Glendale. Cooper went on to fame with his
outrageous makeup and performances, as well as such hits as
``School's Out.''
   The Republican governor, who took office in January 1987, was
recently indicted by a state grand jury for attempting to conceal a
$350,000 campaign loan. Mecham is facing both a criminal trial this
